Title: Tilly Loveseat
Body HTML:
Feel Happy and chic with the Tilly sleeper collection in your home. Fit for a sunroom or a guest room, this sleeper is a perfect companion. Two over two cushion design, accent arm pillows and thin, tapered arms make the Tilly a keeper!

Color: Tophat Buckwheat

Toss Pillow fabric Tophat Buckwheat

DIMENSIONS

55" W x 37" D x 34" H

Title: Chandler 2-Piece Sectional
Body HTML:
You will have all you’ve ever dreamed of with the Chandler upholstery sectional. The entire piece is enrobed with welted detail to create crisp lines. The seat cushions are bordered while the back cushions are T-seat designed. Modern, track arms flow to the wood, tapered, block legs that meet the floor. The Chandler sectional displays a wide, straight front rail border adding a cleaner appearance. Perfect for parties or family gatherings, the Selection sectional doesn’t have a bad seat in the house.

Fabric Color As Shown: Maze Charcoal

Leather Color As Shown: Tempra Gray

Toss Pillows (Fabric Only): Maze Charcoal

 

DIMENSIONS

90"W x 115"D x 36"H

Configuration or Direction of a Sectional: "Left Arm" & "Right Arm" Facing describes the position of the item when you face the furniture (not when you are sitting on it)

Title: Chadoni Server
Body HTML:
Constructed with hardwood solids and Walnut veneers in a smoky gray color finish. Chair seat is covered with a textural woven fabric. Metal accents placed on the chair backs and incorporated into the through leg design offer even more contemporary flavor. The server features sliding doors for unique storage options. Reversible wine/shelf option in the center cabinet and the right and left cabinets have a drawer and adjustable shelf.

DIMENSIONS

72.13” W x 19.13” D x 32.88” H

Title: Altari Queen-Size Sofa Bed
Body HTML:
If style is the question, then this sofa sleeper is the answer. Sporting clean lines and sleek track arms, the decidedly contemporary profile is enhanced with plump cushioning and a chenille-feel upholstery, so pleasing to the touch. Sure to play well with so many color schemes, this sofa sleeper in slate gray includes a pair of understated floral pattern pillows for fashionably fresh appeal. Pull-out queen mattress in quality memory foam comfortably accommodates overnight guests.

Dimensions:

Volume (inch^3): 85" W x 38" D x 37" H.
Weight (pound): 199 lb.
Toss Pillow Side Length (inch): 20".
Arm Height (inch): 26".
Distance Between Arms (inch): 70".
Leg Height (inch):
3".
Mattress Volume (inch^3): 60" W x 72" D x 4.25" H.
Minimum Width of Doorway for Delivery (inch): 32".
Seat Depth (inch): 20".
Seat Height (inch): 20".

Details:

Color: Slate Black | Alloy Gray.
Style: Contemporary, Modern.


  • Corner-blocked frame.
  • Attached back and loose seat cushions.
  • High-resiliency foam cushions wrapped in thick poly fiber.
  • 2 decorative pillows included.
  • Pillows with soft polyfill.
  • Polyester upholstery and pillows.
  • Exposed feet with faux wood finish.
  • Included bi-fold queen memory foam mattress sits atop a supportive steel frame.
  • Memory foam provides better airflow for a cooler night’s sleep.
  • Memory foam encased in damask ticking.

Series Features:

  • Frame constructions have been rigorously tested to simulate the home and transportation environments for improved durability.
  • Components are secured with combinations of glue, blocks, interlocking panels and staples.
  • Seats and back spring rails are cut from mixed hardwood and engineered lumber.
  • Stripes and patterns are match cut.
  • All fabrics are pre-approved for wearability and durability against AHFA standards.
  • Cushions are constructed of low melt fiber wrapped over high quality foam.
  • Sleeper features easy to lift mechanism with memory foam mattress.

Title: Stacey Armchair
Body HTML:
This armchair will fit its way into any setting- cottage, farmhouse, traditional, etc.. A nice tight back and tall tapered legs make this chair very versatile, simple, and casual.

Product Details

  • Product Care: Professional cleaning is recommended. Spot clean only with a water-free dry cleaning solvent. Use caution when using a water-based or detergent-based cleaner, as this may cause water stains or excessive sharing. The water stains may become permanent and impervious to solvent cleaning agents. Do not saturate and do not use water whatsoever. However, to prevent surface soil, recommend that you vacuum or brush lightly to remove dust and grime.
  • Assembly Required: No
  • Weight Capacity: 250 lb.

Upholstered

  • Upholstery Material: 100% Polyester

DIMENSIONS

Title: Altari Sofa
Body HTML:
If style is the question, then this sofa is the answer. Sporting clean lines and sleek track arms, the decidedly contemporary profile is enhanced with plump cushioning and a chenille-feel upholstery, so pleasing to the touch. Sure to play well with so many color schemes, this sofa sleeper in slate gray includes a pair of understated floral pattern pillows for fashionably fresh appeal. Pull-out queen mattress in quality memory foam comfortably accommodates overnight guests.

Dimensions:

Volume (inch^3): 85" W x 38" D x 37" H.
Weight (pound): 131 lb (199 lb Sleeper).
Toss Pillow Side Length (inch): 20".
Arm Height (inch): 26".
Distance Between Arms (inch): 70".
Leg Height (inch):
3".
Minimum Width of Doorway for Delivery (inch): 32".
Seat Depth (inch): 20".
Seat Height (inch): 20".
Sleeper Mattress Volume (inch^3): 60" W x 72" D x 4.25" H.

Details:

Color: Slate Black | Alloy Gray.
Style: Contemporary, Modern.


  • Corner-blocked frame.
  • Attached back and loose seat cushions.
  • High-resiliency foam cushions wrapped in thick poly fiber.
  • 2 decorative pillows included.
  • Pillows with soft polyfill.
  • Polyester upholstery and pillows.
  • Exposed feet with faux wood finish.
  • Included bi-fold queen memory foam mattress sits atop a supportive steel frame.
  • Memory foam provides better airflow for a cooler night’s sleep.
  • Memory foam encased in damask ticking.

Series Features:

  • Frame constructions have been rigorously tested to simulate the home and transportation environments for improved durability.
  • Components are secured with combinations of glue, blocks, interlocking panels and staples.
  • Seats and back spring rails are cut from mixed hardwood and engineered lumber.
  • Stripes and patterns are match cut.
  • All fabrics are pre-approved for wearability and durability against AHFA standards.
  • Cushions are constructed of low melt fiber wrapped over high quality foam.
  • Sleeper features easy to lift mechanism with memory foam mattress.
